quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  43,23,"Ko wano …ďee …óoo fenniri non, …ďe dallinori baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, ko non woniri Men nulaali jertinoowo yim…ďe mun aditaade ma an Nulaa…óo, si wanaa hooree…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen wi'ay: menen men tawu baabiraa…ďe amen …ďen e dow diina, …óum non ko batteeji ma…ď…ďe …óin men jokkata. Haray wanaa e maa woni ko adii e …óum."
  43,24,"Nulaa…óo ma…ď…ďe on maakani …ďe: on jokkay tun baabiraa…ďe mon …ďen, hay si mi addanii on ko …ďuri diina ma…ď…ďe kan mo∆ī∆īude? ∆Āe wi'i: memen dey, ko men yeddu…ďe ko nulida…óon e mun kon."
  43,25,"Men yottii e …óen mofte fennunoo…ďe Nulaa…ďe mun …ďen ado maa, Men halki …ďe. Taskii no battane ma…ď…ďe wa'unoo. Ko battane muusunoo…óe wonunoo."
  43,26,"Janto kadi yo Nulaa…óo, tuma nde Ibraahiima maakannoo ben makko e yime makko …ďen: min on ko mi da…óndii…óo e sanamuuji …ói rewoton …óin, gaanin Allah."
  43,27,"Si wanaa Allah tagu…óo lam On, On …óon fewnay lam e jokkugol diina focciika kan."
  43,28,"O wa…ói konngol tawhiidi ngol Ibraahiima maaki ngol, heddotoongol e …ďaawo makko, ngol mulataa e geyngol wootin…óinoo…ďe Allah …ďen …ďe kafidataa Mo e huunde. Belajo'o, …ďe ruttoray e Allah, tuubugol e sirku e geddi."
  43,29,"Mi hawjaano halkugol …ďee sirkoo…ďe fennu…ďe, Mi dakmitirno …ďe e heddagol e aduna, kam…ďe e baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, haa nde Alqur'aana arunoo e ma…ď…ďe, e Nulaa…óo …ďanngu…óo, woni Muhammadu (Jom kisiyee)."
  43,30,"Nde Alqur'aanaare nden ardirunoo…ďe goonga mo sikke alaa e mu'un, …ďe wi': …óum ko ko Muhammadu woni mbil…óoraade men, menen non, ko men yeddu…ďe …óum."
  43,31,"Sirkoo…ďe fennu…ďe …ďen wi'i: ko hanno Allah jippinira Alqur'aana e gooto e wor…ďe koohoo…ďe Makka maa Taa'ifu …ďen? hara wanaa e Muhammadu baaso alyatimaajo oo?"
  43,32,"E ko kam…ďe senndata yurmeende Joomi maa nden, an Nulaa…óo, sakko wona …ďe okkay nde mo …ďe yi…óani, …ďe …óala nde mo …ďe haaji, kaa ko Allah? Awa ko Menen woni ko senndi arsikeeji ma…ď…ďe …óin hakkunde ma…ď…ďe aduna, Men wa…ói e ma…ď…ďe al…óu…ďe e waasu…ďe, fii no yga ma…ď…ďe wonira eltanaa…ďe …ďeya. Haray, ko ko Joomi maa yurmetee jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen kon ka laakara, …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e dii ko …ďee moo…ďata e aduna lannoowo on."
  43,33,"Si wanaa fii wata yim…ďe …ďen wonu e mofte goote ka keeferaaku, Men wa…óayno e cuu…ói yeddu…ďe Allah …ďen: ki…ď…ďale kaalisi, e Ňčabbir…óe ka …ďe ∆īawra."